Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:14.77,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}任谁都不知
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.77,0:01:18.46,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}在满是人影的街道尽头
