Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:14.23,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}柔らかな　月明かりが照らす 泡沫の雪影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:19.77,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}悴んだ小さな手を合わせ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.89,0:21:25.73,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}透き通る町に微笑む
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:31.14,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}さやぐ时代を全て包み迂んで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.15,0:21:37.44,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}唯 染まる夜に 解き放て
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.51,0:21:40.36,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}降り注ぐ白い花びら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:43.61,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心をそっと解いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:49.15,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}手のひらで溶けて刹那を魅せる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:52.13,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仰ぐ蓝空の彼方に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:55.36,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}行く先の辉映して
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:22:00.09,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}惑いも灯せば良い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:02.99,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}结んだ雪华よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:12.48,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いまに届けと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:14.23,ED_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}柔和的月光映照出那短暂的雪影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:19.77,ED_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}合上那冻僵的小手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.89,0:21:25.73,ED_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}对着通彻的街道 露出甜美的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:31.14,ED_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在痛苦之时包容一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.15,0:21:37.44,ED_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仅仅在那被晕染的夜里释怀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.51,0:21:40.36,ED_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那从天而降洁白的花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:43.61,ED_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}悄悄的触动着我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:49.15,ED_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}看到它在手中融化的那一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:52.13,ED_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仰望着苍穹的远方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:55.36,ED_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}映照出未来的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:22:00.09,ED_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}也照亮我的迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:02.99,ED_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}交错的雪之华
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:12.48,ED_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}现在就想传达到汝心中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是黄昏色的布幕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.22,0:00:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你看 夕阳的余晖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这里是后台
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.79,0:00:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}演完人偶剧之后的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.75,0:00:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}偷偷地 聊着天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在无人知晓的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是诗人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.94,0:00:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}应该差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.73,0:00:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只要能被你拥入怀中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.79,0:00:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}即使是灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:25.25,标题,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,1000)\pos(804,538)}第八章\N\N\h                ‘宛若无法逃脱的诅咒’
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}曾经 我听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}可减缓诅咒执行的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}方法？ 那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}夺走无辜之人的恋情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}啊 所以心中才留下了‘喜欢’这种感情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但却有种很寂寞 无法抑制的想去追求的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没错 萨文蕾提会一直剥夺所有者的恋情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}并计算它的总量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}当超过一定量的时候杀害器官就会发动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:52.06,Default-2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(749,665)}{\blur3}Killing Organ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为别人的恋情也可以发动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真愚蠢呢 人类
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:03:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}吸收他人的恋情 可以暂时地蒙骗计量器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我本以为那孩子吸收他人的恋情 是为了和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只要逃跑就好了 但他却故意出现在你们面前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只要交换身份的话就能混淆我们的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而且 还能使启动延迟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.25,0:03:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是 为什么局限于校内
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那是因为 只要不是青春期的强烈爱恋的话 就没有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}于是 我们被完美地欺骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}以为萨文蕾提逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而你们为了加深犯罪的存在感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}还特意把我叫出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我作为萨文蕾提与你接触
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而萨文蕾提还在远处望风 而这时突然闯入的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有一件事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们为了解除诅咒而行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她为什么知道是这样却还要逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:04:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}比起那种都不知道有没有效果的延缓手段
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}还是和我们一起解除诅咒更…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}居然说要解除诅咒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}对我和萨文蕾提来说 诅咒和恋爱毫无区别
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果解除诅咒 那现在的这份感情会怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}难道说解开诅咒 让我们将这一切都当成一场骗局吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就算这份感情只是出于诅咒 我也不能就这么舍弃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为你是人类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}虽然我其实也不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}喜欢和恋爱什么的 这种人类的心情 是道理说不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}恋爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我还有很多不懂的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果我说了什么伤害了你的那颗心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:04:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}啊 是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}白穗很怕烫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}要不要也吃点仙贝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅现在也不会说不让了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我…我才不要 你别太得意了人类
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}萨文蕾提她…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}萨文蕾提说过的 菲雅是非常好的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}欺骗她让他觉得非常难过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.49,0:05:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}还有 她希望有天可以对那个戴眼镜的女孩子说声抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}并没有什么特别的意义 我要说的就这些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是吗 那家伙说了这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那么夜知 接下来要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这样下去的话 什么事情都解决不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}白穗 我有话想和萨文蕾提说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}昨天我给了他手机 要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我有个想法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}差不多该让我听听你的想法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}锥霞 约定的时间到了没
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}差不多快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}此叶同学 准备得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们可是什么都没透露给我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.77,0:06:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}完全被当成外人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}确实 真让人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}春亮 把手伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那么 萨文蕾提差不多快来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不可能会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}会来的 因为我说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果不来的话就杀了白穗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你搞什么啊此叶 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}结果 人类变成怎样都无所谓呢 道具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是 很遗憾 那孩子不会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}绝对会来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:07:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你们对 白穗 做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}终于来了吗 人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}和电话里说得一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为觉得太麻烦了 所以打算直接毁了你 让一切都结束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这个人类就是为此而下的诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这和约定的不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你在说什么啊 菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}此叶 班长！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为了一方而舍弃另一方这种事  绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}夜知 虽然很明白你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是只能这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}想要…毁掉我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好像已经快坏掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你藏着的猥琐的东西都露出来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你这猥琐的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}已经拼命想把白穗拥入怀中杀掉她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我明白的  我很明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她是那么的美丽 连我也想杀了她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:07:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我是‘箱型恐惧’
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:07:59.90,Default-2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\pos(678,665)}Fear in Cube
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}比你多几十倍的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}可以使人们进入忘我的境界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}学着点吧 人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}结论是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我接下来会杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}开心的杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然后把已经毫无价值的樱参白穗也一并杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}眼看着那样漂亮的脸即将变得丑陋 流着泪大声叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然后求饶 失禁 最终步向死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}别想得逞 别想…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}绝对不会让你杀了白穗的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}第十九号机关
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}抉式螺旋态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}人体钻孔机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}祸动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}下一个就会在白穗身上挖洞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.55,0:08:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}绝不会让你得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}吾以王权诏曰 一切仿造的人偶都将是吾之臣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}服从吧 臣子们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真奇妙 实在是奇妙绝伦了～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你以为这样做就能咸鱼翻身了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}第十八号机关
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.25,0:09:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}伸式外框态
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.09,0:09:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}艾克希特公爵之女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}祸动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}还是不在你身上挖洞了 干脆直接撕裂你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}直到你身体四散为止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不要这样 请不要这样做了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}求你了 别杀萨文蕾提 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}求你了 别杀萨文蕾提 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}求你了 求你了 不管什么我都愿意做 无论是什么都愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}求你别杀了他 求你了 别杀萨文蕾提
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}求你了 要我做什么都好  求你了 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}杀了我也好 不要杀萨文蕾提
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎样了 实现王权的完全人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:46.94,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\pos(714,665)}Sovereignty Perfection Doll
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不会让你杀了她的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不愿意吧 不愿意是吧 非常不愿意对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这样的话你就在这里唤醒你全部的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.53,0:11:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}释放出你体内装置的所有利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}要是你喜欢白穗的话 如果你爱上了他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果那就是诅咒的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就请让我见证这一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这样就结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}白穗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真的结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}白…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}最后绝杀就由你来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你应该知道要做些什么了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}此叶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.86,0:11:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.91,0:11:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}显杀交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}萨文蕾提
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}萨文蕾提
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}白穗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我还以为再也不能和你相见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}很想抱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}虽然是诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是这确实是我发自内心的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以 很想抱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不行 不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}绝对不会放手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只要菲雅加入了队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那么可爱战斗力就会猛增～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.68,0:12:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅没关系的话 我倒是没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}话说 理事长在叫我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}总 总之先告诉我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什么是体育季啊 到底
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.67,0:13:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不好 这莫非是感情交流 文化交流？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那个 简单来说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就像菲雅一样可爱的女孩子们一起蹦蹦跳跳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}让大家感到幸福的活动～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.85,0:13:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.72,0:13:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}蠢毙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那是涡奈的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}啊 拜托了 小菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为了我们舞蹈组的胜利 来 先亲一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嘛 不过菲雅运动神经看似不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}对啊 跳舞什么的很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我知道了 就照涡奈说的做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以放开我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}明天就开始练习 在操场附近的游泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.31,0:13:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}当然 我是抱着必胜的决心的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我诅咒你 人类
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为出现了不少麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}体育季什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}体育季？ 那蠢活动有什么有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}白穗知道什么是体育季吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.83,0:14:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}当、当然知道 这是常识哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}常识…什么？？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}请进 理事长在等着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.09,0:14:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那么 我也应该向你道谢 春亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.67,0:14:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}小菲雅和此叶也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}还有 白穗同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}关于这次的事情 我有话对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}使学生昏迷这件事一定要有个惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以 你的惩罚就是 以后都要来学校认真地学习
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就目前来讲 你是我世界上最讨厌的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.26,0:14:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}变态
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}被如此美丽的女性责备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}对于有某些癖好的人来说 或许是一种幸福啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.64,0:14:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.21,0:14:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好了 接下来给你们看这的东西有两个理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:14:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}第一个是人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以就安排给渐音做助手了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}另一个是渐音的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你们也知道她非常喜欢可爱的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}爱着 LOVE啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是可惜的是 这些都不适合他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以 作为代替 就让…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}理事长 茶已经准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那么 请把那些扯淡的事情都给忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}渐音 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}失 失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.17,0:15:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}原、原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}讨厌 黏黏的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}抱歉 渐音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我太冒失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}啊 有个地方不能视而不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.83,0:15:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是、是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谢谢招待我们吃蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}白穗同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有一点我希望你能记住 你的父亲非常重视你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不知道你是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为什么他要拖着病躯特意把萨文蕾提送到这里来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}想为你做一些事情而不惜做到这种程度 认同一点有何不可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只因他太愚蠢而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}虽然我与他只是偶尔聊聊家常而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}即便如此 有关于你的事情他也未曾不提过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}啊 告诉你一件很重要的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:17:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你曾经因为妈妈的推荐 而加入到一个非常有名的剧团吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}据说 无论是谁都因你的演技而着迷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}倒没什么 我只是按照母亲说的去做而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你爸爸应该去看过你的表演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只是在最初的时候去过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.65,0:17:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}爸爸 那个人对我不曾有过丝毫的关爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}并非如此 你爸爸曾劝说你妈妈让你从剧团退出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}想看见你真正的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他只是不善言语而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你只要记住这一点就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这和我无关
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.43,0:17:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}此叶同学 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.66,0:17:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}啊 别在意 反正已经好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:18:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而且还有认识的其他人偶 也被吸过精气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以非要说的话 也是习惯了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果无论如何都需要恋爱之心的话 请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我会满足你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我想我已经没问题了 但还是感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这个是埋在我身上的 菲雅好像需要这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}送给你 当做谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}免罪符机构
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}诅咒本身还残留着 只是失去了杀害器官而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:37.20,Default-2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\pos(889,665)}Killing Organ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}恋爱着 拥抱着 就是这种感觉哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一直都是这么做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.37,0:18:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嗯 不会输给任何人的程度 从很久之前就是这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.29,0:19:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎么啦 菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不知怎地想起了萨文蕾提和白穗的事情就…该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}心里感到骚动不安 即高兴 又害羞 又羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这是怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.56,0:19:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是在理解以前不理解的事情的途中…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.19,0:19:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你先走吧 我有些事情要跟萨文蕾提说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}女生们的话题 懂了没
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}女生们的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.85,0:19:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我希望你能记住 你的父亲非常重视你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.19,0:19:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}啊 没什么 只是樱参同学笑了 吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我笑了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}啊 抱歉 这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为你实在是太漂亮了 是紧张呢 还是有些怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果有什么隔阂的话 就请直说吧 因为我不太擅长跟人交流
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.46,0:20:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是、是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.09,0:20:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是 像你这样的人 我并不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.63,0:20:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那么 这样我就获得了樱参同学‘第一个朋友’的宝座了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}像朋友那样聊天吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那个…这个… 话题… 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你知道前些日子在学校流传的那件事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果倒下的人被自己喜欢的那个人来探望的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.94,0:20:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好像很快就能恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}还有还有 啊 跟恋爱相关的我就单刀直入的问了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就是说 男朋友之类的 有没？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有个问题希望你告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.70,0:22:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.64,0:22:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你能从我这里吸取吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.05,0:22:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就是说 是否菲雅身体里面有或没的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.47,0:22:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这样啊 从结论上来说 也许存在 也许不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.87,0:22:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什么 那不是没意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.83,0:22:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那菲雅你的愿望是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.20,0:22:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是希望有呢 还是希望没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.00,0:22:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那个 只是想确认清楚而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.90,0:23:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不知道 这个话题就结束了吧 结束了 你也给我忘掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.32,0:23:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}路漫漫其修远兮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.44,0:23:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为了今后着想 给你个建议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.69,0:23:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}也许年龄不一样 重要的并不是时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.15,0:23:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我会为你们两个声援的 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.14,0:23:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们两个？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.80,0:23:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}第九章 归来者的某处不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.05,0:23:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不看就诅咒你哦
